column19: First few satellites in 2024 and full constellation in 2027

16-unit cubesats in 3 planes with about a 12 satellites in each plane. The company plans to launch an additional satellite in late 2021, followed by six satellites and two hosted payloads for the Fast Pixel Network in 2022 and 2023.
